*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZPRG_27_EXCEPTIONS
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zprg_27_exceptions.

START-OF-SELECTION.

  DATA: p_no TYPE i VALUE 10.

  TRY.
      PERFORM sub_check_no USING p_no.

    CATCH cx_sy_zerodivide.
      MESSAGE i000(i8) WITH | Error Zero Divide |.
  ENDTRY.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form SUB_CHECK_NO
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> P_NO
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM sub_check_no  USING    p_no
                   RAISING cx_sy_zerodivide.
  p_no = p_no / 0.
ENDFORM.
